169
00:09:55,338 --> 00:09:56,698
I took you

170
00:09:56,937 --> 00:09:58,657
and your two older brothers

171
00:09:58,817 --> 00:10:00,177
into the palace

172
00:10:00,657 --> 00:10:02,137
to meet the late emperor.

173
00:10:05,858 --> 00:10:08,218
