doesn't matter.

216
00:12:31,378 --> 00:12:32,738
But I believe you will find

217
00:12:32,978 --> 00:12:35,338
a reliable person

218
00:12:35,338 --> 00:12:36,738
to take on the role.

219
00:12:39,218 --> 00:12:39,738
Yes,

220
00:12:40,537 --> 00:12:41,657
I will surely find

221
00:12:41,657 --> 00:12:42,657
